            <p class="description">At Vaibhav Skating Academy, we believe that every skater's journey begins with the right foundation. From learning the basics to building confidence on wheels, our expert guidance and high-quality gear will ensure you have a fun and safe skating experience.</p>
            
            <div class="blocks">
